Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}看似无边无际的海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}让我们心生敬畏 感到惊奇 有时海洋也让我们感到害怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海洋覆盖了地球上70％的表面积{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是这里却是人类最少涉足的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些海浪底下 我的双足底下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}隐藏着那些我们无法想象的生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在革新技术的协助下 如今我们可以进入崭新的世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}用一代人之前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还无法实现的方法来揭示生物的习性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们也认识到了一个令人不快的事实{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们的海洋环境正处于威胁当中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们在以人类历史上前所未有的速度不断变化着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们迎来了一个最紧迫的时期{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们迫切需要揭示海底世界的情况{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在第一集节目中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们将穿过地球 从热带的温暖水域{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}前往极地地区最寒冷的水域{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}以崭新的视角来认识海浪底下的那些生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}欢迎收看《蓝色星球》第二季{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}《蓝色星球》第二季{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一个海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}许许多多海洋生物掩藏在海洋的表面下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过不是所有的海洋生物都被掩藏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}宽吻海豚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们极其聪明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}聪明的宽吻海豚喜欢嬉戏玩耍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}宽吻海豚会冲浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}据我们观察所知 它们这么做纯粹是为了好玩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是要想真正了解宽吻海豚的本性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}你就得紧随它们的步伐 进入它们的世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一小群宽吻海豚来到了红海的一个珊瑚礁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}年纪尚小的宽吻海豚要在这里学习本领{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成年宽吻海豚将一只小宽吻海豚特地带到了一种类似灌木丛的珊瑚旁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这种珊瑚名叫柳珊瑚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}到这里后 成年宽吻海豚变得很怪异{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们故意用身体擦过这些海扇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小宽吻海豚似乎不愿意这么做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是看到长辈们都这么做后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它或许意识到了这是它必须要做的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}事实上 海扇上覆满了一种黏液{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这种黏液具有消炎 抗菌特性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成年海豚这么做或许是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了预防感染{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海豚们对珊瑚礁的详尽了解{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}也驱使着我们前往这里寻找新的药物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}热带珊瑚礁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}仅占海底十分之一的面积{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是由于热带地区的浅水区非常暖和 环境全年稳定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里的生物群落不论是多样性 还是规模{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在海洋里都是首屈一指的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里头的每个生物群落都会让我们有新的发现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}澳洲大堡礁的一种生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}颠覆了我们对鱼类智力的认识{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}猪齿鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}从画面上就可以得知它的名字由来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的行为让人难以相信这是鱼类可以做到的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每天上午它都会游到珊瑚礁的边缘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它要在这些珊瑚碎石和沙子中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}寻找一种特别的食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这儿有一个{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小蛤蜊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过它要如何砸开蛤蜊 吃到里头的肉呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把蛤蜊带回到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}自己的专用厨房里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是它常用的碗状珊瑚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}珊瑚里头有一处特别的凸块{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}没有手的话 处理这个是很困难的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它又丢了一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过它有着坚定不移的决心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和异常精确的技能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}终于砸开了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这儿有条会使用工具的鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些鱼的聪明程度是超乎你的想象的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}热带珊瑚礁的密度非常大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此这里的生存竞争难免异常激烈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}面临竞争的不仅是珊瑚礁内部的生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还有在上空飞翔的鸟类{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在旱季{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}超过五十万的燕鸥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}将会一起涌向这个位于印度洋上的偏僻环礁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些燕鸥雏鸟的黑色羽毛尚未长全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的年龄各异{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}年龄较大的燕鸥奔向天际之时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}另一些还尚未做好准备{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那些刚开始学习飞翔的燕鸥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就把环礁中心的浅礁湖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}当做是训练场地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些燕鸥没法在空中停留太长时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}珍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}珍在捕猎时多是单独行动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过现在有50来只珍从相邻的礁脉来到了这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们是被这里大量的潜在猎物引来的{\r}
