Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.22,0:31:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是因为任何雌鱼的体积一旦长到一个关键尺寸时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.42,0:31:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就会开始发生剧烈的变化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.34,0:31:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在短短几个月内{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.22,0:31:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它体内特定的酶就停止了工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.46,0:31:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雄性激素开始在体内循环{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.10,0:31:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}时间一天天过去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.98,0:31:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的头也开始逐渐变大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.30,0:31:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的下巴变得越来越长{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.26,0:31:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这条雌鱼变成了雄鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.62,0:32:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}此外它的性情也会随之转变{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.06,0:32:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}统治这里所有雌鱼的老雄鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.42,0:32:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}正面临着对手发起的挑战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.10,0:32:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雄鱼的头部越肥大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.66,0:32:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就越能够震慑对手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.30,0:33:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这片领地有了新首领{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.46,0:33:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}只有体型最大的雌鱼才能以这种方式变为雄鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.30,0:33:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过这种转变能让它们拥有更多的配偶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.98,0:33:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这样携带它们基因的后代数量也会大为增加{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.94,0:33:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过新雄鱼可不能太自满{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.26,0:33:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每条雌性金黄突额隆头鱼的体内{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.46,0:33:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都有一条新雄鱼在伺机而动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.74,0:34:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们越接近极地地区 海水的温度就越低{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.22,0:34:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}冰山开始出现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.86,0:34:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}从冰川上脱落的巨大冰块{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.62,0:34:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}正在滑入海中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.46,0:34:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}之后海面开始结冰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.26,0:34:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}极光在上空轻快地晃动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.62,0:34:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就算是隆冬时节{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.06,0:34:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}北极圈的极北地区仍然有几个地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.70,0:34:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}尚未封冻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.26,0:35:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}挪威北部的峡湾尚未结冰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.02,0:35:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是因为浩浩荡荡的墨西哥湾暖流{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.98,0:35:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}从南向北流到了这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.94,0:35:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些水流还将加勒比海地区的暖意一路带到了这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.94,0:35:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每年冬天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.50,0:35:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}数十亿条的鲱鱼来到这里寻求庇护{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.86,0:35:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}跟随鲱鱼前来的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.06,0:35:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还有虎鲸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.26,0:35:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}虎鲸的数量高达一千头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.38,0:35:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这也许是地球上最大规模的虎鲸群{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.42,0:36:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲱鱼的数量纵然很多 但是在这些蜿蜒盘曲的峡湾里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.66,0:36:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}要想抓到它们并不容易{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.82,0:36:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}然而这种虎鲸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.50,0:36:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}却是捕鱼专家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.98,0:36:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}虎鲸们展开团队合作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.34,0:36:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们大声地叫唤彼此 协调行动 逐渐靠近鲱鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.94,0:36:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们将鲱鱼围成了更为紧凑的鱼群{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.50,0:37:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接着它们再游到鱼群底下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.14,0:37:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}将鲱鱼逼到水面上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.46,0:37:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在虎鲸要使出它们的特别武器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.50,0:37:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们用力地拍打自己的尾巴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.58,0:37:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}猛烈的冲击波竟然能把鲱鱼震晕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.06,0:37:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接着 这些失去知觉的鲱鱼便轻轻松松成了虎鲸的囊中之物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.10,0:38:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过这些海底动静也会招来其他动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.82,0:38:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}座头鲸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.14,0:38:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们向这个战场逐渐逼近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.86,0:38:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们从底下靠近鱼群 然后猛地冲向上方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.22,0:38:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}单单一口就能吞下100公斤的鲱鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.34,0:39:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}相对而言 座头鲸算是这里的新来者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.18,0:39:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们不过是在最近十年才开始来到这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.54,0:39:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些极地海洋里的资源实在太过丰富{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.62,0:39:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每只动物似乎都不用愁没食物吃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.66,0:39:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}尽管如此 要是没有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.02,0:40:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}墨西哥湾暖流的话 这里的富饶盛况也就不存在了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.54,0:40:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}事实上 洋流对地球的繁荣昌盛起着至关重要的作用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.18,0:40:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水流将阳光的热量从赤道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.38,0:40:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一路分配至极地地区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.54,0:40:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}让各地都能维持有利于生物生存的气候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.42,0:40:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}从创造气候到产生氧气{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.70,0:40:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海洋在不遗余力地维护地球生态环境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.66,0:40:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过现在却出现了令人担忧的迹象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.22,0:40:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}数千年来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.86,0:41:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一直保持相对稳定的海洋环境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.06,0:41:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如今却在剧烈变化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.74,0:41:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中最为明显的当属北极地区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.50,0:41:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}过去30年来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.58,0:41:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}夏季的冰地面积已经减少了40％{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.30,0:41:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这种突然的暖化现象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.18,0:41:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}多半是人类活动引起的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.34,0:41:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}气候变暖给里野生生物造成了很大影响{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.98,0:41:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海象就是深受影响的一种动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.30,0:41:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每只成年母海象都需要找到一个安全的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.58,0:41:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}让自己那80公斤重的孩子能够休息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.42,0:41:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如今海象惯常的活动区域{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.82,0:42:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海冰正在消融{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.66,0:42:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们只好到陆地上去挤一挤了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.14,0:42:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过这有成百上千只好口角的母亲们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.66,0:42:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些体重近乎达到了一吨 这可不是育儿的理想地点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.82,0:42:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}陆地上的海象有充分的理由要扎堆待在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.86,0:42:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}北极熊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.66,0:42:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成年公海象的体型非常庞大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.98,0:42:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就算是北极熊也很难对付它们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.70,0:42:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}所以北极熊的目标是海象宝宝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.18,0:42:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}北极熊的气味传遍了海象群{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.86,0:43:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海象于是退回到了海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.38,0:43:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}北极熊知道自己没法在海里抓住海象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.58,0:43:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是它自己也有孩子需要喂养{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.70,0:43:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这时一个母亲会如何做呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.62,0:44:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海象母亲还是需要找个地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.58,0:44:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}让自己的孩子们能够好好休息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.86,0:44:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}或许融化的冰山就能满足它的需求{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.42,0:44:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过率先找到这座冰山的并不是它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.06,0:44:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}合适的地方都已经被其他海象占了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.22,0:45:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其他母亲并不愿意腾出地来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.66,0:45:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们也需要有块冰地来保护自己的孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.38,0:45:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}绝望的海象母亲别无选择 只能硬着头皮闯进去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.30,0:45:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一次 大家的希望都落空了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.38,0:46:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}要想在这些融化的海岸上找到个合适的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.62,0:46:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}变得越来越艰难{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.98,0:47:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一同解决这些问题 也使得它们之间的纽带变得牢不可破{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.82,0:47:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此海象母亲的余生都会与自己的孩子保持密切的联系{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.10,0:47:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}可如今谁知道未来会是什么样的呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.50,0:47:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们对海洋生物的复杂性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.98,0:47:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}了解得越多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.62,0:47:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们就会逐渐明白它们的家园是多么的脆弱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.54,0:47:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们的蓝色星球{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.54,0:48:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}幕后集锦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.10,0:48:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}《蓝色星球》第二季在制作上已经投入了四年时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.46,0:48:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}本片的成员前往各个海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.14,0:48:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}寻找不为人知的精彩故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.10,0:48:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中许多故事都是科学界闻所未闻的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.62,0:48:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这使人们对海浪底下的生物也有了新的认识{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.02,0:49:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}准备下去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.30,0:49:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最新的潜水设备不会产生声音和气泡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.70,0:49:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此我们的成员能够在海里更长久 更近距离地观察生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.02,0:49:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们全在你上方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.52,0:49:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}你在空中是拍摄不到这样的画面的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.30,0:49:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了探索最终前沿地带 深海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.74,0:49:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们乘着潜水器在海底一公里处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.26,0:49:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}待了一千个小时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.90,0:49:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}全新的摄像技术{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.38,0:49:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}使得我们能够拍摄人们从未见识过的画面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.38,0:49:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}微光摄像机能够捕捉到人眼几乎无法看到的神奇画面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.16,0:49:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们什么也没看到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.36,0:49:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们是在彻底漆黑的环境下拍摄的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.06,0:49:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们什么也看不见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.90,0:50:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}探头摄像机用全新的视角{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.18,0:50:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}让我们看到了这些微小生物的生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.02,0:50:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.06,0:50:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}吸盘式摄像机则让我们以庞然大物的视角观看海洋的情况{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.18,0:50:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过海洋环境往往变化莫测 在这里工作是非常危险的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.14,0:50:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中最明显的当属南非所谓的“狂野海岸”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.82,0:50:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里是冲浪海豚的栖息之地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.82,0:50:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}摄制团队在这里的任务就是跟随海豚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.26,0:50:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}以前所未有的详尽方式拍摄它们的冲浪行为{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.18,0:50:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里的海洋诡秘莫测{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.46,0:51:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此拍摄团队请了当地的专业冲浪手来当向导{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.58,0:51:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过谁也没料想到今年的海浪竟然会这么大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.86,0:51:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一情况对冲浪摄影师克里斯布莱恩来说十分棘手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.50,0:51:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}对 我是挺紧张的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.54,0:51:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海上的涌浪非常大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.54,0:51:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}真的很大 那海浪好像有六米多高{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.94,0:51:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}对 这估计是我这辈子遇上的最大的巨浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.18,0:51:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}看来不冒险就没有收获{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.18,0:51:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}克里斯准备了一部高速摄像机{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.10,0:51:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}用来拍摄海浪里的超慢镜头画面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.46,0:51:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}摆在他面前的难题是 他要尽可能地靠近破浪而行的海豚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.86,0:52:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}好消息是他们在地平线处看到了海豚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.06,0:52:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他们说这是今年最大的涌浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.26,0:52:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}嘿 我从来没见过这种画面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.38,0:52:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这比我想象中要大多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.10,0:52:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}置身于这些海浪当中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.50,0:52:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}要想靠近海豚唯一的办法就是驾驶喷气式滑橇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.90,0:52:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他们仅是迂回前行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.78,0:52:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就很困难了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.90,0:53:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}好在驾驶员对海面情况了如指掌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.06,0:53:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最后总算带着他们安全穿过了这些巨浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.18,0:53:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}可他们还是没见到海豚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.14,0:53:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}拍摄成员只好在惊涛骇浪当中穿行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.42,0:53:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}回到海岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.42,0:53:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就是这样 快点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.02,0:53:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}怎么样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.62,0:53:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}真是太刺激了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.62,0:53:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海浪接触到了滑橇的尾部{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.66,0:53:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我就一直喊着“快离开这里 琼斯 快离开这里”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.10,0:53:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}猛地撞了一下 我要紧紧抱着摄像机{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.70,0:54:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}差点没给晃到海里去 单单是从海里驶出来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.86,0:54:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就让人紧张不已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.10,0:54:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这对我来说已经是家常便饭了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.66,0:54:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}第三天 情况突然发生了大转变{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.86,0:54:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海上出现了很多海豚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.42,0:54:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海面也平静多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.74,0:54:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在海上基本上看不到什么海浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.10,0:54:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们会来的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.98,0:54:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在大多数情况下 如果你知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.94,0:54:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}自己所在的海洋位置是对的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.94,0:54:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那你只需要耐心等候时机的到来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.78,0:54:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一周后狂野海岸马上又要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.94,0:54:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}迎来一场风暴 激浪变得越来越凶猛{\r}
